data.description: Copper Cove is a secluded, gated neighborhood located off of Paluxy Drive in Tyler with 1 and 2 acre lots. It is an amazing location for country-living atmosphere while still being close to the city. Copper Cove is inside the Tyler city limits and is in close proximity to hospitals, offices, and schools. It is zoned for Whitehouse ISD. The streets are built to the City of Tyler specifications, and utilities are underground, including gas, electric, telephone and cable/internet. The City of Tyler provides Copper Cove with water and sewer services. Copper Cove is deed restricted and has a Homeowners’ Association. Build your dream home here!
